1. JCEpop standard size

    870px x 522px

2. image width standard

    640px

3. Element anywhere (younique code)

    {yoonique_item: 611 element: Text}

4. image size for the banner

    1025 x 284

5. image size for the teaser

    760 x 220
    
6. youtube autoplay, put at the end of the link of single video embed

    ?autoplay=1 

7. youtube autoplay, put at the end of the link of playlist video embed

    &amp;autoplay=1

8. insert zoo article using shortcode

    {zooitem:145 text: Increasing impact: a checklist}
    
    {zooitem:611 text: Read more...}

9. id name for factsheet printing header

    id="factsheetstyling"
    
10. Image caption

        <figure><img src="YOUR IMAGE LINK" />
            <figcaption style="width: GET THE IMAGE WIDTH IN PX">CAPTION GOES HERE.</figcaption>
        </figure>
        
        use style="width: 200px; float: right; clear: both; on figcaption if image is aligned right or left. see example below.
        
        <figcaption style="width: GET THE IMAGE WIDTH IN PX; style="width: 200px; float: right; clear: both; ">CAPTION GOES HERE.</figcaption>
        
        
11. Make slider open from links to another page.
    
    adding &slider=SLIDERNUMBER and ?slider=SLIDERNUMBER
    on the URL address. SLIDERNUMBER is slider number that begin counting from 1,2 etc...
    see example below.

    www.mydomain.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=123&slider=1
    or
    www.mydomain.com/some/page?slider=2
    
12. External link class name (to display the external icon near the link.)

    external-link
    
13. Iframe sample using source

    {source}<iframe src="fsf/Alkalinity.htm" width="100%" height="800"></iframe>{/source}
